Processes

INVENTORY
1. Create new box and sent to box queue
2. Review previous box stats
3. CRUD ramen, brands, box

ORDERS
1. Customer creates new order
2. Customer registers
3. Customer pays order
4. Create a new Stripe token
5. Create a new Stripe customer
6. Subscribe Stripe customer to subscription plan
7. If no errors, mark current month's order paid and customer subscribed
8. Order checks for address verification and shipping rate

SHIPPING
9. Order sent to shipping queue
10. Order marked shipped
11. Order complete

FINANCES
12. 30 days later customer charged
13. Reloop order process

CUSTOMERS
1. LTV
2. Churn-rate